Class DMItem

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--edu.rosehulman.soar.datamap.items.DMItem
Direct Known Subclasses:
DMEnumeration, DMIdentifier, DMNumericItem, DMString
public abstract class DMItem
extends java.lang.Object

Abstract class to represent any item in the datamap. I probably should have named it DMAttribute, but it is far too late to change that now.

Author:
Tim Jasko
